[SHORT DESC]
The target cannot switch out.

[LONG DESC]
<p>The target cannot switch out. The effect is lost when the user switches. Mean Look ignores all accuracy and evasion modifiers. Cannot prevent the target from escaping with Baton Pass, U-turn, or the item Shed Shell.</p>

<p>The effect of this move is Baton Passable (both on you and your opponent).</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/block">Block</a> is identical.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/spider_web">Spider Web</a> is a Bug-type equivalent.</p>